metadata.name: Open To The Public
metadata.description:
For this piece, I set up my canvas and paint pens at a local music and art event, and had random passerby’s add whatever they felt to the canvas. Then I taped over the contributions I wanted to remain, and began painting. 
.
This method brings a more intimate and inviting atmosphere because everyone gets to feel invested in the piece, they’re all a part of it. Not to mention how fun it is to see their drawings preserved in the final piece, I love it. A collab with a whole party. 
.
